            video me plan&egrave;, ac sentio restitu[m]. Sin"/>
        <underline method="pen" type="straight" language="LA" text="sed etiam monimentum praebet inimico doloris mei, sceleris sui, publice calamitatis: quis erit ui hunc"/>
        
